title: The Gate Restaurant
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Organic, Juice bar, Beer/Wine, British, English, Indo-Iraqi
description: Offers casual vegetarian dining with Indo-Iraqi Jewish influence. All-day mezze bar menu and weekend brunch. Vegan options are marked "vo." Located opposite Saddler's Wells Theatre, around the corner to Upper Street, and a short walk from Angel tube station.
